            <NUMEX TYPE="CARDINAL">1</NUMEX>. The <ENAMEX TYPE="PER_DESC">press</ENAMEX> is treating <ENAMEX TYPE="GPE">Jackson</ENAMEX>'s chief conclusions--that <ENAMEX TYPE="ORGANIZATION">Microsoft</ENAMEX> has
