            <NUMEX TYPE="CARDINAL">3</NUMEX>. That's not to downplay the <NUMEX TYPE="CARDINAL">one</NUMEX>-sidedness of the findings of fact.
Although <ENAMEX TYPE="PERSON">Jackson</ENAMEX> did credit <ENAMEX TYPE="ORGANIZATION">Microsoft</ENAMEX> with helping accelerate the expansion of
the Internet and with benefiting <ENAMEX TYPE="PER_DESC">consumers</ENAMEX> via innovation in other cases, the
weight of his ruling is on the side of the <ENAMEX TYPE="ORG_DESC">government</ENAMEX>. In particular, his
